LatticeFold+ Verifier — License & Provenance
============================================

SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT

Copyright (c) 2025-2026 The Soqucoin Core developers

Original work by Soqucoin: a clean-room implementation of a LatticeFold-style
folding verifier for constant-size Dilithium batch verification. Licensed under
the MIT License; the full license text is in the repository root `COPYING`.

This module implements a published cryptographic construction; it is not derived
from third-party source code. Portions were rewritten as part of the Halborn
Extension Audit remediation (see the SECURITY NOTE headers in the source).
